rows.label: qst201401_0010
rows.name:
Huh? You're telling me we're
staying here for the night?

rows.label: qst201401_0020
rows.name: Yes. Is there a problem?

rows.label: qst201401_0030
rows.name: A huge one!

rows.label: qst201401_0040
rows.name:
A dreary place like this will
totally drain my Girl Power!

rows.label: qst201401_0050
rows.name:
What is "Girl Power", mo? And
what it has to do with inn, mo?

rows.label: qst201401_0060
rows.name:
Girl Power is the indispensable
power needed for a girl's battles!

rows.label: qst201401_0070
rows.name:
If it's low, you could say
that a girl can't even...

rows.label: qst201401_0080
rows.name: ...continue to live as a girl!

rows.label: qst201401_0090
rows.name: Oh! So it is that important, mo!

rows.label: qst201401_0100
rows.name:
All inns are the same. It's not
like there's much of a difference.

rows.label: qst201401_0110
rows.name: ...You're being too dramatic, Zakuro.

rows.label: qst201401_0120
rows.name: I'm not being dramatic!

rows.label: qst201401_0130
rows.name:
In a place like this, you can't even
do your skincare routine properly!

rows.label: qst201401_0140
rows.name: Or what?

rows.label: qst201401_0150
rows.name:
Are you fine being near Rex with your
skin in such a sorry state, Hikari?

rows.label: qst201401_0160
rows.name: Sorry...state...?

rows.label: qst201401_0170
rows.name: Who are you calling sorry-skinned?!

rows.label: qst201401_0180
rows.name: Oh, my apologies.

rows.label: qst201401_0190
rows.name:
I guess since your Girl Power was low
to begin with, you don't notice, huh?

rows.label: qst201401_0200
rows.name:
Hey, hey, Rex, you'd rather have
me around than Hikari, right?

rows.label: qst201401_0210
rows.name: What? Is that so, Rex?

rows.label: qst201401_0220
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Huh?

rows.label: qst201401_0230
rows.name: Uh... well... I wonder?

rows.label: qst201401_0240
rows.name:
Whoops, look at that. The boy
looks like he's about to cry...

rows.label: qst201401_0250
rows.name:
Nia, shouldn't we stop this
before it gets complicated?

rows.label: qst201401_0260
rows.name: Huh? N-No way.

rows.label: qst201401_0270
rows.name:
Getting between those two right now
would be suicide, wouldn't it?

rows.label: qst201401_0280
rows.name: I'll leave it to Turtle-chan.

rows.label: qst201401_0290
rows.name: Don't be an idiot...

rows.label: qst201401_0300
rows.name:
If I stick my neck into this kind of
problem, it'll only get more complicated.

rows.label: qst201401_0310
rows.name: ...Ah, so you are self-aware.

rows.label: qst201401_0320
rows.name: Then we have no choice but to watch...

rows.label: qst201401_0330
rows.name:
It's just playful banter. It
won't become a major issue.

rows.label: qst201401_0340
rows.name:
Besides, your sense of style
is so old-fashioned, Hikari.

rows.label: qst201401_0350
rows.name: How can you wear something so moldy?

rows.label: qst201401_0360
rows.name: Was that in style 500 years ago?

rows.label: qst201401_0370
rows.name: M-Moldy?!

rows.label: qst201401_0380
rows.name:
And you! Aren't you embarrassed wearing
an outfit that covers so little?

rows.label: qst201401_0390
rows.name: Huh? Look who's talking!

rows.label: qst201401_0400
rows.name:
...All right. In that
case, it's a competition.

rows.label: qst201401_0410
rows.name:
Let's settle once and for all
who has more Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201401_0420
rows.name: Ooh, sounds interesting.

rows.label: qst201401_0430
rows.name:
Then, as a penalty, the loser has to perform
the latest dance craze for everyone.

rows.label: qst201401_0440
rows.name: Well? Do you have the guts to accept?

rows.label: qst201401_0450
rows.name: Of course.

rows.label: qst201401_0460
rows.name:
The winner is already decided, but
are you really sure about this?

rows.label: qst201401_0470
rows.name: I'm sure.

rows.label: qst201401_0480
rows.name:
My victory is certain, but I'll
play along to kill some time.

rows.label: qst201401_0490
rows.name:
Um... don't you think you should
stop? Fighting isn't good.

rows.label: qst201401_0500
rows.name: Rex, you stay out of this.

rows.label: qst201401_0510
rows.name: ...Yes, ma'am.

rows.label: qst201401_0520
rows.name: The competition starts at 18:00.

rows.label: qst201401_0530
rows.name:
Until then, we should both prepare
to show off our Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201401_0540
rows.name: Fine by me.

rows.label: qst201401_0550
rows.name: Understood. That's fine.
